Engineering OS process-guard: stage-artifact exemption.

This repo predates the artifact-chain pipeline (contract -> critique -> frozen
acceptance suite -> implementation). This marker disables ONLY the
stage-artifact check, so src/** changes are not blocked on a
test/acceptance/acceptance.manifest.json that does not exist yet.

freeze-hash and mixed-diff still run normally.

The marker is a deliberate, visible gap: it is listed in every Engineering OS
audit. It comes out when the first frozen acceptance suite lands (the ratchet in
engineering-os/ONBOARDING.md).

Reference: https://github.com/acartag7/engineering-os
